</P>
<P>
   Public opinion, monitored almost bomb-by-bomb, kept an
indisputably tight rein last year on NATO's military strategy.
</P>
<P>
   Russia has turned the lesson of the Persian Gulf and Kosovo
inside out: With public support, a war can thrive. And so in
