agents, they failed to sign one of their own free agents -
defensive end Chuck Smith. Smith blames the Falcons for not making
an offer and the organization counters that Smith didn't accept an
offer that was presented to him. A look at how and why Chuck Smith
left the team. (Winkeljohn, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 15.
