<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-02-26 22:47 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9871 &Cx1f; taf-z
u s BC-BKN-NETS-HORNETS-NYT &LR;      02-26 0756
